Package com.intellij.psi.util

Enum JavaElementKind

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<JavaElementKind>
      • com.intellij.psi.util.JavaElementKind
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<JavaElementKind>

    public enum JavaElementKind
extends java.lang.Enum<JavaElementKind>
    Represents a kind of element that appears in Java source code. The main purpose of this enum is to be able to display localized element name in UI
